data.description: Stunning condo with an open floor plan. As you walk in the front door you are greeted by beautiful kitchen with white cabinets, stainless steel appliances, a pantry, and plenty of space to meal prep! It is open to the living room with tons of natural light from a large window and glass door to the patio. Easy access outside for BBQ's! Main level primary suite with dual sinks and a large soaking tub, plus private door to the patio. Upstairs there are two good good sized bedrooms that share a full bathroom with dual sinks and soaking tub. There is also a loft that makes a great place to relax, and laundry room. Plenty of space to for parking and storage in the two car garage. Exterior was recently painted. Great community pool!
